SECTION(EXIT STATUS)
On success, returns zero.  On failure, returns non-zero.

SECTION(EXAMPLES)

To create and use a CODE(FUSE) mount point for access to remote chirp servers:

LONGCODE_BEGIN
% chirp_fuse /tmp/chirp-fuse &
% cd /tmp/chirp-fuse
% ls
% cd host:port
% cat foo/bar
% exit
LONGCODE_END

